INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3490516652, 'officer_flavor_text_34004', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> ENGINEERING
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> UNIMATRIX TWELVE
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> NONE

A respected scientist among Vulcans, Stonn is another to have fallen victim to the Borg’s control, alongside his partner T’Pring. Stonn’s dedication to protecting his family became meaningless once he was chosen and abducted for the sake of assimilation. As Four of Eleven, the former geologist and surveyor seems doomed to a life of fulfilling the whims of the Borg, and the peaceful future he once envisioned for his family now a distant memory.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3490516652, 'officer_name_34004', 'Four of Eleven', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
