INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3583932904, 'officer_flavor_text_106', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> ENGINEERING
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> UNIMATRIX TWELVE
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> NONE

No amount of ferocity, determination or fighting spirit will save you when the Borg come. Jaylah learned this lesson the hard way. The once soft spoken Starfleet cadet, who so famously survived alone against Krall and his Swarm had finally met a foe she could not evade. She was taken, along with several other of her fellow cadets and subjected to the horrors of Borg assimilation. As the last remnants of her free will were robbed from her, she cried a single tear. Not for herself, but for the friends she would be forced to hurt.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3583932904, 'officer_name_106', 'Five of Eleven', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (3583932904, 'officer_name_short_106', 'FIVE OF ELEVEN', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
