<color=#40FF60>{1:#,#%}</color> chance of adding 2 shots to each weapon when fighting Borgs

<color=#309BBF>Strengthen the Unimatrix</color>
<color=#40FF60>+{2:#,#%}</color> to the Health of all Officers on the ship', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
