INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (423029416, 'officer_flavor_text_140', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> SCIENCE
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> TOS ENTERPRISE CREW
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> FEDERATION

Leonard “Bones” McCoy was born in Georgia, USA in 2227. He studied medicine in the mid 2240s in Mississippi, where he gained a reputation as a practical joker. His steady hand and impeccable memory made him a naturally gifted doctor, and when he joined Starfleet, quickly rose through the ranks and gained a position on the flagship of the Federation, the Enterprise. There, he took on the role of Chief Medical Officer and Head of Life Sciences.
McCoy is a regular volunteer for away team excursions and has been involved in many large-scale medical operations that have saved multiple civilizations from outbreaks and serious ecological disaster.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (423029416, 'officer_name_140', 'TOS Leonard McCoy', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (423029416, 'officer_name_short_140', 'TOS MCCOY', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
