INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (1683164967, 'officer_flavor_text_149', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> SCIENCE
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> TNG CREW
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> FEDERATION

Although he’s one of the most advanced technologies in the universe, in both his mental and physical abilities, what’s most remarkable about the USS Enterprise-D’s resident android officer is his humanity. Throughout his many adventures and challenges with the Enterprise crew, he has shown curiosity, a sense of humor, and even compassion. Furthermore, he often engages in the most human of hobbies, such as painting and reading.
While many have questioned whether or not Data can be considered a truly sentient being due to being an A.I., those who know him best believe that he is truly alive, having seen first hand his growth, both as an officer and as a friend.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (1683164967, 'officer_name_149', 'Data', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (1683164967, 'officer_name_short_149', 'DATA', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
